ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Must-take for everybody, interested in Metrics
I definitely recommend. It is a very advanced class but a unique opportunity to learn about a relatively new field in econometrics and learn directly from the best scholar in the field.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course topics were totally new, so I learned a lot

This course was very influential on my research. I intend to apply the methods learned on this class on my research project and continue to study sieves methods. I don't believe this class can be taught in many if any top graduate programs. I intend to continue studying this field and I believe the opportunity to learn directly from prof. Chen is already a differential, it already puts me in a great position. I am also very thankful to professor Chen for her advice during classes and office hours.
Yes. This is a course that will be useful for my research !
